<span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">DKL</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">q</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">_</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.167em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∥</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.167em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">]</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 3.199em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.15em 0px 0px 0px; text-align: right;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: 0.775em;"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.15em 0px 0px 0px; text-align: left;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: -0.18em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">log</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 3.988em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 3.988em; top: -1.59em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 3.988em; bottom: -1.09em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 3.988em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.68em; vertical-align: -1.09em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">]</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">]</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>对给定模型进行预测并根据后验进行采样是不可交换的——不可能在不改变结果的情况下将期望值移入或移出上述对数。因此，我们得到两种不同的预测方法和两种不同的泛化误差。</p><h1>有界概括</h1><p>在推导泛化边界时，我们不仅要决定要限制<i>哪个</i>泛化度量，还要<i>决定如何</i>限制它。主要有以下三个决定：</p><ol><li> <strong>“全球”还是“本地”</strong> ？您希望结果适用于整个权重集还是特定权重选择？</li><li><strong>依赖于数据集还是独立于数据集</strong>？您是否希望结果适用于您的特定样本集或所有可能的数据集选择？</li><li><strong>均匀、平均还是概率</strong>？您希望该界限始终保持平均状态，还是以某种最小概率保持不变？</li></ol><h2>全球与本地</h2><p>第一个也是最重要的问题是是否要限制整个模型类的泛化误差，还是仅限制特定模型的泛化误差。经典学习理论采用全局方法。现代深度学习理论采用了更本土化的方法。奇异学习理论提出了第三种<i>介观</i>方法，该方法可以获得模型<i>子类</i>的泛化界限。</p><p><strong>全球范围</strong>。全局方法是最坏情况的方法。上限必须适用于所有模型，因此它只与最差泛化模型一样严格。查找这些最坏的情况通常涉及询问模型类对随机噪声的适应程度如何。在纯随机噪声上训练的模型根本无法泛化，因为没有信号，因此完美拟合随机噪声意味着最坏情况的泛化误差是可怕的。这将泛化变成了表达能力的问题，这是通过<strong>VC 维度</strong>、 <strong>Rademacher 复杂度</strong>和<strong>覆盖数</strong>等复杂性指标来操作的。</p><p>因为神经网络通常可以完美地适应噪声，所以根据这些测量，它们非常复杂，并且结果边界变得<strong>空洞</strong>：它们简单地预测测试误差将小于 100%。</p><p>我们在实践中观察到良好泛化的原因是，并非一个类中的所有模型都同样复杂。例如，权重修剪的成功表明许多权重可以安全地设置为零并消除。因此，平均泛化可能与最坏情况泛化有很大不同。</p><p><strong>局部边界</strong>。您可以研究特定模型对噪声的鲁棒性，而不是研究模型类表达噪声的能力 - 应用于输入的噪声（<strong>边际理论</strong>）、应用于权重的噪声（<strong>最小锐度/平坦度</strong>、<strong>压缩理论</strong>），或应用于训练样本的噪声（<strong>算法稳定性和鲁棒性</strong>）。为了获得泛化界限，可以将这些对噪声的经验鲁棒性替换为对新数据的预测鲁棒性。</p><p>尽管这些结果带来了真正的改进，但界限仍然太宽松，无法解释大型的现实世界模型。即使对于 MNIST，测试误差百分比的最佳上限也比我们在最先进模型中实际观察到的大一个数量级。进展最终会赶上吗？还是这些限制反映了这种方法的更根本问题？ </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/zcguehgktxwepa6ylikb" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/efyd9xzpcdjmx05jlseb 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/a2ofnleq15kjargchgmh 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ugo81wjk4n6nxoulbblw 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/hxsnbqp4ldn6hfyvqae8 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/kr6ltjzyetq5hsuldfx0 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/xqo62hjjuuzuvoywhkx2 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/cxm5y7aofeis5kz3tyzm 1470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/tokkmeudmmal1nds3hr9 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ugq9wq6deknfzmljmgz5 1890w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/zljtbpcixzhx3vgjml7c 2032w"><figcaption>来自<a href="https://proceedings.neurips.cc/paper_files/paper/2022/hash/cbeec55c50c3367024bafab2438a021b-Abstract-Conference.html">洛特菲等人。 (2022)“PAC-Bayes 压缩界限如此紧密以至于可以解释泛化”</a> ：这些分类错误的界限（较低 = 更好）仍然或多或少是最先进的。星号<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\star"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋆</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>表示使用数据相关先验（见下文）。尽管其中一些界限是非空洞的（即，比 100% 更严格），但它们距离有效地限制大型现实世界系统还很远。还有很多概括需要解释。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>介观边界</strong>。您可以研究学习模型的<i>分布</i>如何响应噪声，而不是研究<i>单个</i>模型对噪声的反应程度。换个角度来看，这将研究泛化变成了比较模型<i>子类</i>的问题。</p><p>这种观点已经隐含在深度学习理论领域中，这些领域获得了涉及<strong>权重范数</strong>、<strong>压缩</strong>、<strong>最小锐度/平坦度</strong>以及各种<strong>信息论量的</strong>泛化界限。它在奇异学习理论中得到了明确的体现，提出了一组用于研究模型复杂性和泛化性的规范可观测量，例如<strong>学习系数</strong>、<strong>奇异波动</strong>和<strong>多重性</strong>。对于理想化的贝叶斯学习器，SLT 预测大数据限制下贝叶斯和吉布斯泛化误差的<i>值</i>（不仅仅是上限）。</p><h2>数据集依赖性</h2><p>第二个问题是是否限制给定数据集或跨可能数据集分布的泛化误差。实际上，我们只有一个数据集，并且想要了解模型如何针对该特定数据集进行泛化。从理论上讲，通常更容易边缘化对特定数据集的依赖。</p><p>边缘化数据集通常是合理的，因为我们更感兴趣的是模型在大量数据的限制下如何执行。在这些限制下，任何单个数据点的影响都会消失。然而，在分布具有较厚尾部（例如 RL）的情况下，此假设可能不成立。</p><h2>泛化边界的风格</h2><p>最后一个问题主要是美学问题：我们如何打扮我们的界限？由于泛化由数据和权重组成，因此这分为两个子问题：如何修饰数据上的界限以及如何修饰权重上的界限？</p><p><strong>统一界限</strong>。最强的界限是在模型类上<i>一致</i>成立的界限，即涉及全称量词的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n(f_w) < \epsilon,\quad \forall w\in\mathcal W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 1em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∀</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∈</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-cal-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em; padding-right: 0.046em;">W</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>这是相对于<i>权重</i>定义的，因为我们很少对数据集中一致的界限感兴趣。除了平凡的分布之外，总是存在病态的数据绘制，表现出较差的概括性。</p><p><strong>概率界限。</strong>较弱（从某种意义上说，它们并不总是成立）但通常更严格（上限较低）是“概率”成立的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb P(G_n(f_w) < \epsilon) > 1-\delta."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">P</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.007em;">δ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>尽管可以制定相对于权重分布的概率界限，但实际上，这些界限总是相对于数据分布来定义。</p><p><strong>期望界限</strong>。 “预期”的界限仍然更弱但更紧。这些是在对权重/数据集取期望值后保持的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb E[G_n(f_w)] < \epsilon."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">]</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>与通常保留给权重的统一界限和通常保留给数据的概率界限不同，期望界限在更平等的基础上对待权重和数据。</p><p><strong>结合界限</strong>。有了这些选择，就可以混合搭配。由于这些运算是不可交换的，因此您可以交换顺序以使边界加倍。改变潜在概率分布的选择，不同泛化界限的可怕数量会进一步增加。为了稍微简化问题，通常可以将一种格式的边界转换为另一种格式。</p><h2>命名的界限族</h2><p>许多关于如何绑定和绑定什么的选择的特定组合都有专用的名称。不幸的是，这些名称既不详尽，也不排他，也不一致。</p><p>几个比较重要的：</p><ol><li><strong>均匀收敛</strong>：在数据集绘制的概率上限制<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，并均匀地覆盖模型<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="w \in\mathcal W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∈</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-cal-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em; padding-right: 0.046em;">W</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的所有可能选择以及数据生成分布<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="q(x, y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的所有可能选择。</li><li><strong>可能近似正确（PAC）</strong> ：对于特定的数据生成分布，在数据集<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="D_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的绘制上以概率绑定<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，并在模型类上均匀分布。</li><li><strong>平均近似正确 (MAC)</strong> ：在联合分布的期望中限制<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。换句话说，绑定<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb E_{p(w,D_n)}[G_n]"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="p