据可以让您更加确定您正在尝试学习的功能，因此有必要学习更复杂的拟合。这意味着我们需要一个相对于我们所看到的数据量来定义的复杂性概念。</p><p>在本节的其余部分中，我们将单独检查该表达式中的每个术语。之后，我们将看到这个公式如何导致子类方面的视图泛化。</p><h3>学习系数</h3><p><a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/6g8cAftfQufLmFDYT/you-re-measuring-model-complexity-wrong">正如我之前所说</a>，学习系数是模型复杂性的“正确”概念（至少在贝叶斯设置中）。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:86.72%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/tepqfpucxdimy1fmnigz" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/i9xa1nljymvlci1etz07 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/itdwtbnic51vx7b4asvt 240w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/agab07ycgt0mjouao8b7 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/orxjh6jl5ybyocckr17c 480w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/jotpdsjlklnmdvoxa1ha 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/eygmpwxwc0nsgrksl0qg 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/xlt8uwaj8rxpukvrvwmi 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/crizavnu8cq4eqthjua1 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/nswt1i7fqjnl02c5hqyd 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/d7i3jwtgoh7qbeoeaqgk 1182w"><figcaption>学习系数测量当你沿着损失图向下移动时权重空间体积的变化率。</figcaption></figure><p>以下是我们目前所知道的：</p><ul><li>学习系数是<strong>自由能公式中的第二项</strong>，</li></ul> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-ch