le="margin-right: -0.007em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.007em;">β</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: -0.262em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.007em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.007em;">β</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: -0.262em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>除此之外，目前人们对奇异波动及其对现实世界系统的意义知之甚少。</p><h3>多重性</h3><p>学习系数之后，重数<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="m"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">m</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>控制下一个主导项 ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\log\log n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">log</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">日志</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ) 在自由能公式和两个泛化误差中。所以它对泛化的影响小于学习系数。</p><p>与奇异波动一样，人们对它在现实世界系统中的作用知之甚少。与单一波动不同，多重性的含义相对简单。给定一个在某个点<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>消失的多项式，当使用以<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>为原点的坐标系时， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x 处的重数是 x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">中</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>最低阶项的次数。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/rzmbkowonsm4lp5zy01a" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/bsdvzy1islvfxn3icsgy 130w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/vhlflt47aubfya9zz08z 260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/b1qudlfgm0sf1prh7qgz 390w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/arn8awzinxydgogxeyhi 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/vucesuifbypubivor3to 650w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/mjwijysge7g0wsdrguoo 780w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/alfr9guo4dqwktbx55in 910w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/qggvsuvsezpqozijeibu 1040w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/cxxu1lw24o6il4vhisbl 1170w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/qeeq5nnvgp6zvbh1qok6 1284w"><figcaption>原点处重数为 2 的曲线。<a href="https://www1.maths.leeds.ac.uk/~pmtemf/files/BFK_Frobenius.pdf">贝尼托等人。 (2012)</a></figcaption></figure><h3>体重标准</h3><p>权重范数可能是显式参数计数作为模型复杂性度量的最明显的替代方案。众所周知，权重衰减等正则化术语鼓励更简单的模型，从而更好地泛化。当然，学习理论家一直在努力获得涉及正则化强度和权重规范的界限（例如，参见<a href="http://proceedings.mlr.press/v40/Neyshabur15.pdf">Neyshabur et al. 2015</a> 、 <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1712.06541">Golowich et al. 2019</a> ）。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:80.77%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/qtyrhv609cmawt6bvzso" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/mcz9wzwrz3qfbgemogvr 220w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/oslhlcsqajkeqr1rtmt4 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/sv2tfowsrxrsksss2v0c 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/zt5j7gaylzi1osc96fai 880w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/fsz4ayaotn0tqavdv9sg 1100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/hhuwmgqmi5qribnpjxsb 1320w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/njpy8ijo0zqzgdcngw4m 1540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ayxjmbgkpw8a80xqlqqn 1760w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/pis3lil142jlg9ewrtm5 1980w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/enruixsoxtfkpoiulcxe 2124w"><figcaption>更大的重量标准预算可以实现“更尖”的合身。这两条曲线是彼此的常倍数。哪个“更简单”？</figcaption></figure><p>不幸的是张等人。还考虑测试神经网络是否可以<i>在正则化存在的情况下</i>拟合随机噪声。它们可以，这意味着仅权重范数不足以解释观察到的泛化性能。纳入体重标准可能会导致更严格的限制，但这些只是边际改进，不足以解决这个谜团。</p><p>形式上，这是因为权重范数对自由能的贡献比学习系数和多重性低。在多重性项之后，有一个与数据集绘制的随机性相关的随机项<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="F^R(\xi)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.106em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.106em;">F</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.266em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.005em;">xi</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和一个包含先验贡献的常量阶项<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="o_p(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">o</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。通过选择高斯先验的标准，这就是权重范数出现的地方。因此，权重范数对行为和泛化有影响，但比您在贝叶斯设置中预期的要小。</p><h1>泛化热力学</h1><h2>内部选型</h2><p>最后一组复杂性度量在什么意义上与模型子类相关？</p><p>为了揭示这种联系，让我们将权重空间粗粒度化为覆盖<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathcal W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-cal-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em; padding-right: 0.046em;">W 的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>紧凑子集<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="W_\alpha"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.104em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.104em;">W</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的集合。目前，分区的具体选择是任意的（ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=60Sd0D-D960&amp;list=PL4vaU_gO_6LJctKxh0BfZ05gK-LLnlgTM">取决于一些技术条件</a>）。这使我们能够将自由能<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="F_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.106em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.106em;">F</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>重新表示为每个子类的<i><strong>局部</strong></i><strong>自由能</strong><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="F_n(W_\alpha)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.